        <item>
            <title>1.11.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>Content grows up into a real post planner.</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>A dedicated Content space</b> — posts are now their own thing, fully separated from your tasks and agenda (no more content cluttering other areas)</li>
                    <li><b>The composer is the post</b> — write on glass, attach photos, and <b>record sounds</b>, add tags, set a platform (Instagram / Bluesky) and a schedule, all in one sheet</li>
                    <li><b>A queue you can see</b> — drafts, scheduled, and posted flow through a vertical pipeline, with a week strip for what's coming up</li>
                    <li><b>Lifecycle</b> — Draft &#8594; Ready &#8594; Scheduled &#8594; Posted, with a one-tap "mark posted" (auto-publishing comes later)</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
